                  Paragraph(body=RichText('Key finding: self-attention mechanisms outperform recurrent approaches for\nlong-range dependency capture (sequence length > 512 tokens). The O(n²) memory\ncost of full attention remains a practical bottleneck for very long documents.\n')),
